   "mainEntity": [
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "Who is the best electropolished pipes manufacturer in Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Sakshi Forge is among the most trusted electropolished pipe manufacturers serving Mumbai. Unlike traders, we manufacture in-house, so every pipe carries a guaranteed Ra ≤0.4 µm internal finish, EN 10204 3.1 mill test certificate and PMI verification. We supply pharmaceutical and petrochemical units across Mumbai - including Andheri MIDC - with dispatch in 3-7 working days and manufacturer-direct pricing."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "What is the price of electropolished pipes in Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Electropolished pipe prices in Mumbai depend on grade, OD, wall thickness and finish level. As an indication, SS 304L EP pipe typically starts around ₹280-₹380/kg and SS 316L around ₹380-₹520/kg, with sanitary A270 tubing priced per metre. Because Sakshi Forge is the manufacturer, Mumbai buyers save 8-15% versus trader rates. WhatsApp your size list for a firm same-day quotation - prices are locked for 7 days."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "Which grades of electropolished pipes are available in Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "We stock and manufacture EP pipes in SS 304, 304L, 316, 316L, 316Ti, 321, 347, 904L and duplex 2205 for Mumbai customers. 316L is the standard choice for pharmaceutical and high-purity applications; 304L suits dairy and food lines; duplex and 904L handle chloride-rich or aggressive media. Our team helps Mumbai buyers pick the right grade against their process fluid, temperature and cleaning regime."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "What sizes of EP pipes and tubes can you supply to Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "We supply electropolished pipes from 1/8\" NB to 24\" NB (6 mm to 600 mm OD) in schedules SCH 5S through SCH 160, plus sanitary tubing to ASTM A270 in 1/4\" to 4\" OD. Seamless and welded (bead-removed) construction are both available, in standard 6-metre lengths or cut-to-length for your Mumbai site, with capped and poly-sleeved ends."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "What surface finish do your electropolished pipes achieve?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Our standard electropolished finish is Ra ≤0.4 µm (16 µin) on the internal surface, with Ra ≤0.25 µm (10 µin) available for semiconductor and WFI applications. Every batch is measured with a calibrated profilometer and the Ra report ships with the material - so your QA team in Mumbai receives documented proof, not just a claim."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "Which industries in Mumbai use electropolished pipes?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "In Mumbai, electropolished pipes are specified by pharmaceutical, petrochemical and food processing units - anywhere product purity, corrosion resistance or cleanability is critical. Typical applications include WFI and purified-water loops, clean steam lines, CIP/SIP circuits, high-purity gas distribution and hygienic product transfer lines in facilities across Andheri MIDC and Chembur industrial belt."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "Do you deliver electropolished pipes to industrial areas in Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Yes. We deliver across Mumbai and the wider Maharashtra region, including Andheri MIDC and Chembur industrial belt, with door delivery to your plant or site store. Standard stock dispatches in 3-7 working days; project quantities are scheduled to your construction timeline. Every consignment is transit-insured, and the LR copy and e-way bill are shared on WhatsApp the moment material leaves our works."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "Do you provide mill test certificates (MTC) with EP pipes?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Yes - every supply carries an EN 10204 Type 3.1 mill test certificate covering chemical composition and mechanical properties, plus PMI verification of the heat. On request we provide IGC (intergranular corrosion) tests, NABL-approved lab reports, hydrostatic/eddy current test records and third-party inspection - the documentation package Mumbai's regulated pharmaceutical projects need to clear audits."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "What is the minimum order quantity for Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "For standard EP pipe sizes, we accept orders from a single 6-metre length for Mumbai customers - useful for maintenance and small skid jobs. Custom sizes, non-standard grades and special finish levels (Ra ≤0.25 µm) carry a modest MOQ, typically 50-100 metres, which our team confirms with your quotation."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "How fast can you deliver electropolished pipes to Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Ready-stock sizes reach Mumbai in 3-7 working days from order confirmation. Custom lengths, special grades or large project lots typically ship in 2-3 weeks depending on quantity. For shutdown and emergency requirements, we offer priority dispatch - call +91 82913 66340 and our Mumbai desk will confirm the fastest possible date before you place the order."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "Can I order flanges and fittings along with EP pipes in Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Absolutely. Sakshi Forge manufactures forged flanges (ASME B16.5/B16.47), butt weld fittings (B16.9), forged fittings (B16.11), stainless steel seamless pipes, round bars and plates. Mumbai buyers routinely combine EP pipes with matching-grade flanges and fittings on one PO - one MTC set, one delivery, and zero grade mismatch at the joint."
     }
    },
    {
     "@type": "Question",
     "name": "How do I get a quote for electropolished pipes in Mumbai?",
     "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Three ways: (1) WhatsApp your size list or BOQ photo to +91 82913 66340 - fastest, quotes within 2 business hours; (2) email sakshiforge1737@gmail.com; (3) use the enquiry form on this page. Mention 'Mumbai' and your delivery pincode so freight is included in the first quote itself. Bulk, project and annual-rate contracts are quoted separately with locked pricing."
     }
    }
